            <abstract>
                <p>Qǝne poem. The type is indicated in the manuscript as <foreign xml:lang="gez">mawaddǝs</foreign>. According to 
                    <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/C92MK42D"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Guidi1900Qene"/><title level="a">"Qenê" o inni abissini</title><title level="j">Atti della Reale Accademia dei Lincei, Rendiconti, Classe di scienze morale, storiche e filologiche</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Ignazio</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Guidi</t:surname></author><date>1900</date><biblScope unit="volume">Serie quinta, 9</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">463-510</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">4-5</citedRange></bibl>, it is a 
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">mawaddǝs za-kʷǝllǝkǝmu</foreign>-type with nine verses. The name of the author is not indicated.</p>
            </abstract>
